snippet.title: The Second Reality Project 2 "R" Trailer
snippet.description:
This is the second trailer for
"The Second Reality Project 2 - Zycloboo's Challenge" v2, which is a remake of the hack with the same name released in 2006. Like with the Teaser trailer I released 2 years ago, the music remix comes again from Nethy The Dragon.
